{"tid":1411894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[8.5 三罷集會] [重要] 交通疑難排解集中區","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:06:38.000Z","uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"137e2d9c233d94ee052d008b54219b1720a02dda","tid":1411894,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:51:00.000Z","msg":"罷工 IS NOT 放假，唔好忘記七區集會！<br />\n<br />\n不過明白宜家交通唔方便，見到好多手足求救話揾唔到方法去集會地點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>所以不如我地出個集中 post <br />\n交通上有咩困難擺曬上黎問<br />\n條條大路通羅馬，肯定有手足答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已出發手足都歡迎提供可行路線</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/05/124817_596ff1d9376085cdcb47b3e6884dd289.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2F124817_596ff1d9376085cdcb47b3e6884dd289.png&h=694b6b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41U8PD7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41U8PD7.gif&h=d7eac3f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9ee76af10d9a9b821eba1ac224584aecf0f43fe","tid":1411894,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"推上去，幫下各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bf9e0a38951adcf5d316f99fe66f1b4941b9d5","tid":1411894,"uid":107985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"天星小輪有冇服務？想過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddc7ab8ca1b550e6e67e16b1dc09948388f033d","tid":1411894,"uid":31024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b0ef5c83a618ddad99e6e9d4ddcd1662721e99a","tid"